From: Manish Goregaokar <manishearth@google.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Feb 2026 23:07:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] [temporal] Implement new specced reference year behavior

Uplift of https://github.com/unicode-org/icu4x/pull/7640
and https://github.com/unicode-org/icu4x/pull/7641

The spec cleared up how it expects reference years to work, especially
around "nonexistant" MonthDay combos in Chinese/Korean. This updates
ICU4X to that latest spec text.

Bug: 401065166
